WEBVTT

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.296
Birds are my passion,

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:37.696
and I want to change the way
each one of you thinks about them.

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:41.280
The easiest reason I love them so much
is because they are beautiful.

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:45.616
There are 10,000 species in the world,

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:49.000
and each one of them
is uniquely beautiful.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:51.680
Birds are amazing,

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:56.176
and this talk is dedicated
to all the birds of the world.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:57.776
(Laughter)

00:01:57.800 --> 00:02:01.536
(Applause)